headline: Did GoDaddy's (GDDY) AI Identity Launch Just Redefine Its Digital Ecosystem Ambitions?
summary: GoDaddy recently launched a trusted identity naming system for AI agents, leveraging established internet security protocols such as DNS and X.509 certificates to streamline verification and interoperability across agent frameworks. This move highlights GoDaddy's effort to shape industry standards for digital identity management in AI, expanding its influence beyond traditional domain services.
